{"type": "article", "id": 2906, "title": "可实现立体收纳的炊具组合", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-17T08:04:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232341hi2e896jQD0CE3YB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t设计师 Vacimi 近日推出了一系列小巧而精致的全功能组合炊具，包含两个平底锅、一个汤锅、一个蒸盘以及两个玻璃锅盖。可堆叠的设计使得整套炊具可以实现立体收纳，有效节省了厨房空间。而锅面部分的菱形图案设计是为了让底部的燃烧均匀发散，玻璃锅盖中间的可翻盖手柄的设计，则可以帮助用户实现蒸汽压力的自由控制。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232338cIBY2lJydCTsDiKe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232338Mmi9OYn1IALxEHyc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052323393OzVNULy75hfR0mG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232339EDY7qTzuoa3x8MlQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232340A4DxJqOiSycGdBYm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}